    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <https://data.vlaanderen.be/id/concept/dataserviceprotocol/OGC:WCS-2.0.0-http-get-coverage>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/PUBLIC>;
    <http://data.europa.eu/r5r/applicableLegislation> <http://data.europa.eu/eli/reg/2009/976/oj>;
