    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoCoverageAccessService>, <https://metadata.vlaanderen.be/id/GDI-Vlaanderen-Vlaamse-Administratieve-Eenheden/Vlaams%20Gewest>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
