<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#4dbcc3182d12e380e55616795f90b9a4>.
<#4dbcc3182d12e380e55616795f90b9a4> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://publish4.geo.be/geodcat/collections/main/items/48234430-44ba-11ed-a201-7478273ff935>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-06-15T15:38:11.024Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#4dbcc3182d12e380e55616795f90b9a4> {
<https://publish4.geo.be/geodcat/collections/main/items/48234430-44ba-11ed-a201-7478273ff935> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "48234430-44ba-11ed-a201-7478273ff935";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Open Maps for Europe (Discovery Service)"@en, "Open Maps for Europe (Service de recherche)"@fr, "Open Maps for Europe (Zoekdienst)"@nl, "Open Maps for Europe (Suchdienst)"@de;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "This is the discovery service of the pan-European spatial datasets provided by the European mapping and cadastral agencies: EuroGlobalMap, EuroRegionalMap, EuroDEM, Open Cadastral Map, Pan-European Imagery, Open Gazetteer. The datasets are openly available accessible on the platform Open Maps for Europe (OME) http://www.mapsforeurope.org/."@en, "Ce service assure la recherche des jeux de données géolocalisées pan-européennes fournies par les agences cartographiques et cadastrales européennes: EuroGlobalMap, EuroRegionalMap, EuroDEM, Open Cadastral Map, Pan-European Imagery, Open Gazetteer. Les jeux de données sont ouvertes et disponibles sur la plateforme Open Maps for Europe (OME) http://www.mapsforeurope.org/."@fr, "Dit is de zoekdienst van de pan-Europese spatiale datasets die door de Europese cartografische en kadastrale agentschappen worden verstrekt: EuroGlobalMap, EuroRegionalMap, EuroDEM, Open Cadastral Map, Pan-European Imagery, Open Gazetteer. De datasets zijn open en beschikbaar op het platform Open Maps for Europe (OME) http://www.mapsforeurope.org/."@nl, "Dieser Dienst führt die Suche nach europaweite Geodatensätze, die von den europäischen Kartierungs- und Katasterbehörden bereitgestellt werden: EuroGlobalMap, EuroRegionalMap, EuroDEM, Open Cadastral Map, Pan-European Imagery, Open Gazetteer. Die Datensätze sind frei zugänglich auf der Plattform Open Maps for Europe (OME) http://www.mapsforeurope.org/."@de;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/type> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceType/discovery>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/created> "2022-10-05"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2022-10-05"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#date>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <https://org.belgif.be/id/CbeRegisteredEntity/0216755012>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/conformsTo> <http://www.opengis.net/def/serviceType/ogc/csw>;
