<#377c8420da8cfb0f132e2b6c4b009d0b> {
<https://publish4.geo.be/geodcat/collections/main/items/35682bee-261c-11e9-b42c-14abc58d5215> a <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#DataService>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/identifier> "35682bee-261c-11e9-b42c-14abc58d5215";
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "CORINE Local Components (WMS)"@en, "CORINE Local Components (WMS)"@fr, "CORINE Local Components (WMS)"@nl, "CORINE Local Components (WMS)"@de;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "CORINE Local Components is an INSPIRE compliant WMS service showing 4 \"Local component products\" covering the Belgian territory within the framework of a Pan-European coverage. The 4 layers cover 4 different products: Urban Atlas 2012, Urban Atlas 2012 Street Tree Layer, Riparian Zones and Natura2000."@en, "CORINE Local components 2012 WMS est un service WMS conforme à INSPIRE illustrant 4 'Local component products' occupant le territoire belge dans le cadre d’une couverture paneuropéenne. Les 4 couches portent sur 4 produits différents : Urban Atlas 2012, Urban Atlas 2012 Street Tree Layer, Riparian Zones et Natura2000"@fr, "CORINE Local Components WMS is een INSPIRE conforme WMS service die 4 \"Local Component Products\" toont die het Belgische grondgebied overdekken in het kader van een pan-Europese overdekking. De 4 lagen hebben betrekking op 4 verschillende producten: Urban Atlas 2012, Urban Atlas Street Tree Layer, Riparian Zones en Natura2000."@nl, "CORINE Local Components WMS ist ein INSPIRE-konformer WMS-Dienst, der 4 'Local Component Products' anzeigt, die das belgische Landgebiet innerhalb von einer pan-europäischen Deckung abdecken. Die 4 Schichten betreffen 4 verschiedene producten: Urban Atlas 2012, Urban Atlas 2012 Street Tree Layer, Riparian Zones und Natura2000."@de;
