    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <https://www.geo.be/thesaurus/rpi.xml>, <https://www.geo.be/thesaurus/mwr.xml>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/national>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoMapAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/ac>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/ef>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/hh>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3144>;
