    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/rights> <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/86b3bc916fe847f9ad506b8ede128fcb956-1704000472e0a4cc>, <http://data.gov.be/.well-known/genid/86b3bc916fe847f9ad506b8ede128fcb956-1704000472e0a4d0>;
