    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#servesDataset> <https://publish4.geo.be/geodcat/collections/main/items/65132770-71dc-11eb-b166-3448ed25ad7c>, <https://publish4.geo.be/geodcat/collections/main/items/63b98ade-71dc-11eb-8bf5-3448ed25ad7c>;
