    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/ge>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/8>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/23>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5270>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5277>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/11226>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/12666>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7882>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/12665>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/8167>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/4108>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/2333>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7298>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5288>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3650>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3780>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7843>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoProductAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
