    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/tn>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/37>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/11276>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/8641>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5116>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/11277>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/12135>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoProductAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TRAN>;
