    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/gn>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/14902>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5545>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/10203>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/9382>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/6743>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/1912>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5360>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5523>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoProductAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/REGI>;
