    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/SOCI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/HEAL>;
