    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/sd>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/8>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/10073>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7982>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoProductAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
