    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/ps>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/4>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/23>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/11>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5494>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/4648>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5520>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/6740>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/2470>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5538>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5507>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/11061>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/6376>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3974>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5513>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/1700>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5498>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/530>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5523>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5360>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/3650>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/1912>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/6743>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoMapAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/REGI>;
