    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/bu>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/5>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/11312>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/1029>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoProductAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
