    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/lc>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/35>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/2>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/4213>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/78>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/4641>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/8797>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/8820>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/9297>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/7143>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/13164>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoMapAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/AGRI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/ENVI>;
