<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#52dc9a50eded9f8b545a3798df3abf7f>.
<#52dc9a50eded9f8b545a3798df3abf7f> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://geodata.wallonie.be/id/efb63d5f-a019-47ee-8899-bc12ad3891c2>;
