    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/el>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/15>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/16>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/2195>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/10140>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoMapAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#theme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/REGI>, <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/data-theme/TECH>;
