    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/subject> <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/theme/ef>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/32>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/theme/11>, <http://www.eionet.europa.eu/gemet/concept/5352>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialDataServiceCategory/infoProductAccessService>, <http://inspire.ec.europa.eu/metadata-codelist/SpatialScope/regional>;
